{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325730/extras/fireball_final.gif?t=1738075285\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>The Hive</i> is a strategy game with RPG elements where you assume command as the insectoid hive mind. Set in a vast, ancient underworld filled with forgotten civilizations, colossal creatures, and untold mysteries, your journey is one of survival, evolution, and uncovering the secrets of a lost world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As your colony grows, so does your understanding of the ruins scattered across New Eden, revealing a tragic history and a glimpse of what lies beyond. In this hostile yet beautiful landscape, danger and discovery go hand in hand, and every choice could shape the fate of your swarm.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325730/extras/vivade01a_top.png?t=1738075285\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">MAIN FEATURES  </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Assume control as the insectoid hive mind and lead your swarm to survive and thrive in a vast, ruined underworld.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325730/extras/waterfall01a.gif?t=1738075285\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Build and expand your underground nest to create a thriving colony and powerful forces.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Harvest DNA from defeated enemies to unlock new units, abilities, and strategies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Equip your creatures with powerful items scavenged from the remnants of lost civilizations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325730/extras/gameplay_banner_01.gif?t=1738075285\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Battle massive ancient creatures and adapt your strategy to overcome evolving challenges.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience an epic story that spans the hostile, yet captivating, underworld of New Eden.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325730/extras/gameplay_banner_03.gif?t=1738075285\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore a beautiful yet dangerous world filled with ancient civilizations, mysterious ruins, and hostile creatures.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover diverse biomes, from serene blooming springs to fiery volcanic regions, each filled with unique beauty and peril.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325730/extras/gameplay_banner_02.gif?t=1738075285\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Slaughter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/325730/bca32a1daf61c8b8d63ff4232d60b9a439c58b7b.jpg"},{"name":"Massacre","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/325730/26480b1b9421b05e76458cb8c3cae886ee6ce237.jpg"},{"name":"Orb of Wisdom","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/325730/d0363673207c42084998375090cf9176b260f8b5.jpg"},{"name":"The Artifact","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/325730/cc12664f96b4587b9e42349022e81d2a5f91ad9e.jpg"},{"name":"The Sunken City","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/325730/31168349d4ad826426c775b7688a2564a7d14218.jpg"},{"name":"The Avatar","path":"https:/